# Used by the `web` service's Docker build, which needs repo-root context to reach
# apps/docs/content/docs/guide (see infrastructure/docker/docker-compose.yml and
# apps/web/Dockerfile). Keep this scoped to what actually bloats/pollutes that build context —
# apps/docs/content itself must NOT be excluded here.

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.source
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.git
.claude
screens
styleguide
references
